						               													<description>Remnant is a build your character card game where you build your character by buying and selecting cards of your choice to prepare your character for the final epic battle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2-6 players&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn, you roll the dice. Moving your character holder that many spaces in the direction of your choosing. Resolve what you land on to collect cards or coins. Once completed you have the opportunity to buy cards for your character. Once you have 3 features or 3 characteristic cards you can no longer buy those until you have 3 of the opposite.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose the cards you want and even replace cards if you get the same types. Once you become a full character you can even buy weapons and armor to deck out your fantastic creation, giving you attack and defense benefits as well as special interactions with different cards on other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Find your opponent to attack and roll a dice to multiply your attack or defense.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Final circle occurs when all players become a &amp;quot;full&amp;quot; character. This forces battle after battle in a brutal all out war.&amp;#10;Last one standing wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
